source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000010_GAIA<tab>I'm drawing out the Darkness. Get ready!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000020_RYNE<tab>It worked, Gaia! We've done it!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000020_RYNE<tab>やったねガイア、成功したよ！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000030_RYNE<tab>So this all took place a hundred years ago...
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000040_RYNE<tab>But what does it have to do with Gaia?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000040_RYNE<tab>ガイアの記憶と、どう関係が……？

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000050_RYNE<tab>I know this place...! It's the gaol in Eulmore!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000050_RYNE<tab>これは……ユールモアの監獄棟！？
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000060_RYNE<tab>たとえ何が立ちふさがろうとも……

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000070_RYNE<tab>...we will never give up hope!

target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000080_EDEN3BOSS3<tab>我が娘の征く明日に  祝福を……
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000090_EDEN3BOSS4<tab>二度と分かたれることのないよう……。

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000100_EDEN3BOSS4<tab>One that we may share for all eternity.

target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000110_RYNE<tab>まだ、彼女の意識は残っているはず……

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000120_RYNE<tab>I won't give up on our future, Gaia! No matter what!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000120_RYNE<tab>必ず、一緒に明日を迎えよう……ガイア……！
